-- Banca Marche Is in Talks With Groupama on Buying Stake, Chairman Tells MF
-- Chiara Remondini
-- 2010-06-22T06:34:48Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/banca-marche-is-in-talks-with-groupama-on-buying-stake-chairman-tells-mf.html

          
          
             Banca delle Marche SpA is in talks
with French insurer Groupama to sell a stake in the Italian
regional lender, Chairman Michele Ambrosini told newspaper  MF .  
 The two financial institutions exchanged “letters of
intent,” Ambrosini said. He added Banca Marche got six to seven
expressions of interest including from Vienna Insurance Group
and a unit of Assicurazioni Generali SpA.  
          
          


  


        